===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[Catholic]] [[sacrament]] of [[Holy Communion]].
# {{by extension}} A [[Catholic]] [[religious]] [[service]] in which this sacrament is enacted.
# The substances received during this sacrament, namely the bread and wine, seen as Christ’s body and blood.

